{"word":"G4215 - ποταμός - potamós - pot-am-os' - Flood","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ποταμός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>potamós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pot-am-os'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Flood"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வெள்ளம், நதி, ஆறு, நீரோட்டம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a stream, a river"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably from a derivative of the alternate of <a href=\"#/G4095 - πίνω - pínō - pee'-no/4095\">G4095</a> (compare <a href=\"#/G4224 - πότος - pótos - pot'-os/4224\">G4224</a>); a <i>current</i>, <i>brook</i> or <i>freshet</i> (as <i>drinkable</i>), that is, <i>running water:</i> - flood, river, stream, water."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4215 - ποταμός - potamós - pot-am-os'/4215\">G4215</a>, <a href=\"#/G4216 - ποταμοφόρητος - potamophórētos - pot-am-of-or'-ay-tos/4216\">G4216</a>"}]}